[
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "47",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\"><st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">This</st> <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">was</st><n id=\"1\" /> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\">Lord</st></span>\u2019s <st data-num=\"01697\" class=\"\">message</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> the <st data-num=\"05030\" class=\"\">prophet</st> <st data-num=\"03414\" class=\"\">Jeremiah</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">about</st> the <st data-num=\"06430\" class=\"\">Philistines</st> <st data-num=\"02962\" class=\"\">before</st> <st data-num=\"06547\" class=\"\">Pharaoh</st> <st data-num=\"05221\" class=\"\">attacked</st> <st data-num=\"05804\" class=\"\">Gaza</st>:<n id=\"2\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "1"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "47",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">\u201c<st data-num=\"03541 0559 03068 02009\">Look</st>! Enemies are gathering in the <st data-num=\"06828\" class=\"\">north</st> like <st data-num=\"04325\" class=\"\">water</st> <st data-num=\"05927\" class=\"\">rising</st> in a river.<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">They will <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">be</st> like an <st data-num=\"07857\" class=\"\">overflowing</st> <st data-num=\"05158\" class=\"\">stream</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">They will <st data-num=\"07857\" class=\"\">overwhelm</st> the whole <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">country</st> and <st data-num=\"04393\" class=\"\">everything</st> in it like a flood.<p class=\"poetry\">They will overwhelm the <st data-num=\"05892\" class=\"\">cities</st> and their <st data-num=\"03427\" class=\"\">inhabitants</st>.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0120\" class=\"\">People</st> will <st data-num=\"02199\" class=\"\">cry out in alarm</st>.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">Everyone</st> <st data-num=\"03427\" class=\"\">living</st> in the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">country</st> will <st data-num=\"03213\" class=\"\">cry out in pain</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "2"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "47",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"01\" class=\"\">Fathers</st> will <st data-num=\"06963\" class=\"\">hear</st> the <st data-num=\"08161 06541\">hoofbeats</st> of the enemies\u2019 <st data-num=\"047\" class=\"\">horses</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">the <st data-num=\"07494\" class=\"\">clatter</st> of their <st data-num=\"07393\" class=\"\">chariots</st> and the <st data-num=\"01995\" class=\"\">rumbling</st> of their <st data-num=\"01534\" class=\"\">wheels</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">They will <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"06437\" class=\"\">turn back</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> save their <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">children</st><p class=\"poetry\">because they will be <st data-num=\"07510\" class=\"\">paralyzed</st> with <st data-num=\"03027\" class=\"\">fear</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "3"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "47",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">For</st> the <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">time</st> has <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">come</st> <p class=\"poetry\">to <st data-num=\"07703\" class=\"\">destroy</st> <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> the <st data-num=\"06430\" class=\"\">Philistines</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">The time has come to <st data-num=\"03772\" class=\"\">destroy</st> <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> the <st data-num=\"05826\" class=\"\">help</st><p class=\"poetry\">that <st data-num=\"08300\" class=\"\">remains</st> for <st data-num=\"06865\" class=\"\">Tyre</st><n id=\"1\" /> and <st data-num=\"06721\" class=\"\">Sidon</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">For</st> I, the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>, will<n id=\"3\" /> <st data-num=\"07703\" class=\"\">destroy</st> the <st data-num=\"06430\" class=\"\">Philistines</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">that <st data-num=\"07611\" class=\"\">remnant</st> that came from the <st data-num=\"0339\" class=\"\">island</st> of <st data-num=\"03731\" class=\"\">Crete</st>.<n id=\"4\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "4"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "47",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">The people of <st data-num=\"05804\" class=\"\">Gaza</st> will <st data-num=\"0935 07144 0413\">shave their heads</st> in mourning.<p class=\"poetry\">The people of <st data-num=\"0831\" class=\"\">Ashkelon</st> will be <st data-num=\"01820\" class=\"\">struck dumb</st>.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"05704\" class=\"\">How</st> <st data-num=\"04970\" class=\"\">long</st> will you <st data-num=\"01413\" class=\"\">gash</st> yourselves to show your sorrow,<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">you who <st data-num=\"07611\" class=\"\">remain</st> of Philistia\u2019s power?<n id=\"2\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "5"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "47",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">How long will you cry out,<n id=\"1\" /> \u2018<st data-num=\"01945\" class=\"\">Oh</st>, <st data-num=\"02719\" class=\"\">sword</st> of the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\">Lord</st></span>,<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"05704\" class=\"\">how</st> <st data-num=\"0575\" class=\"\">long</st> will it be <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">before</st> you <st data-num=\"08252\" class=\"\">stop killing</st>?<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0622\" class=\"\">Go back</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">into</st> your <st data-num=\"08593\" class=\"\">sheath</st>;<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"07280\" class=\"\">stay there</st> and <st data-num=\"01826\" class=\"\">rest</st>!\u2019<n id=\"3\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "6"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "47",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">But <st data-num=\"0349\" class=\"\">how</st> can it <st data-num=\"08252\" class=\"\">rest</st><n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">when I, the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>, have<n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"06680\" class=\"\">given</st> it <st data-num=\"06680\" class=\"\">orders</st>?<p class=\"poetry\">I have ordered it <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> attack<p class=\"poetry\">the people of <st data-num=\"0831\" class=\"\">Ashkelon</st> and <st data-num=\"0413 02348 03220 08033 03259\">the seacoast</st>.\u201d<n id=\"3\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "7"
  }
]